{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent08TextAreaB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:spaces:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/TextAreaComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of text area"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextArea"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TextAreaComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for text area component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text area component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingBlockXl }","        override var sizeMinHeightInput: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._1000 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: TextAreaComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own space and size semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider/TextAreaComponentTokens-Implementations":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider\/textareacomponenttokens-implementations","title":"TextAreaComponentTokens Implementations","type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/TextAreaComponentTokens-Implementations"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"sym